<p class="doc-para">We may also process your personal data with your consent (e.g., for direct marketing purposes). If the processing is based on the consent, you can withdraw your consent any at time by contacting us by email at <a href="mailto:team@afrk50.com">team@afrk50.com</a>. Please note that withdrawal of consent does not affect the lawfulness of processing based on consent, which took place before the withdrawal of consent. 
