<p class="doc-para">AFRK50 is the authorized data processor, however we may use carefully selected service providers (authorized data processors) to process your data. By doing so, we would remain fully responsible for your personal information.  We may use the following categories of data processors: data collectors, management and storage providers, e-mail service providers, pop-up service providers, customer relationship management and feedback service providers, direct marketing service providers, payment service providers, accountants, legal and other advisers. 
</p> 



