</h2>
<p class="doc-para">All Users and AFRK50 will have access to your personal data as per our General Terms and Conditions.
</p> 
<p class="doc-para">We may also share your personal data with our trusted services providers when they provide services to us or to you on behalf of us and under our instructions. We will control and shall always remain responsible for the use of your personal data. 
</p> 
